<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154510" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3">This Status bar field uses the same measurement units as the rulers. You can define the units by choosing <link href="text/shared/optionen/01070500.xhp" name="Tools - Options - Presentation - General"><emph>Tools - Options - %PRODUCTNAME Impress - General</emph></link>.</paragraph>
